-- Turkey Urges Preparedness for Possible Syria Chemical Attack
-- B y   S e l c a n   H a c a o g l u
-- 2013-09-04T08:35:28Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-09-04/turkey-urges-preparedness-for-possible-syria-chemical-attack.html
Disaster Management Authority, known
in Turkish as AFAD, urges citizens to turn room in their house
into shelter in case of possible chemical attack.
* NOTE: U.S.-ally Turkey, which sided with Syrian rebels in
their quest to topple Syrian President Bashar al-Assad, fears
chemical attack by Syria if U.S. launches strikes  To contact the reporter on this story:
